{
  "text": "Then an O-D trip matrix is estimated from the AADT values. In traffic models one well-known problem is the trip matrix estimation, where some observations (link flows) are taken and the O-D flows are estimated [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] [CITATION_7] Zhang, 1999 or Yang et al., 1992) .",
  "correct_citation": {
